snippet.title: White Hell Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the demo now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1378360/White_Hell/
https://kelesoft.itch.io/white-hell-demo

Enter White Hell, a retro-style first-person shooter where a lone survivor, Jarmo, wakes up on his toilet floor after hibernating through the apocalypse and has to fight his way through the frozen wastelands of Finland controlled by opposing extremist groups. 

Trailer by: Antti Allén

https://twitter.com/WhiteHellGame
